task.summary: Got the first post going! Added multiple post functionality, for that matter. Along with some async refactoring and js for curly quotes!
Some improvements for speed, along with post edits.
Made post links a bit more elegant
Added some sort-of-gross css and js to stop the page jumping around while the header image loads.
Added some simple css for plot sizing on phones
Sunset gifs are coming! The beginnings of the post and the backend api.
I think we should be ok...
Changes to reduce image size (hopefully this will reduce bandwidth?)
Switched to python 3.10, updated libraries, and switched from aiohttp to httpx
